(316,	27,	5,	2,	'Mild and Rain season. The climate is comfortably warm. The rain season is starting. Who likes nature, likes the rainy season. But, it takes a little time for the rainfall to produce effects on nature. This period is often called the Green season. In mountainous areas, the rains are generally more intense, and some showers may occur in the afternoon, so this area is usually covered by rainforests. This month is a good time to visit mountains but the best option.',	'Мягкий и дождливый сезон. Климат комфортно теплый. Начинается сезон дождей. Этот месяц является хорошим временем для посещения гор, но не самым лучшим вариантом.'),
