(318,	27,	7,	1,	'Green season. It\'s also mild and rain season, so nature recovered its most beautiful assets to welcome you. The climate is comfortably warm. In mountainous areas, the rains are generally more intense, and some showers may occur in the afternoon, so this area is usually covered by rainforests. It\'s best time to visit mountains, so the treks lovers will also prefer to come to travel in Thailand this month.',	'Зеленый сезон. Это мягкий и дождливый сезон, но это лучшее время для посещения гор. Климат комфортно теплый. '),
